What was my total income and total amount spent for June - August?

SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN category_id = 1 THEN amount ELSE 0 END) AS total_income,
	   SUM(CASE WHEN category_id != 1 THEN amount ELSE 0 END) AS total_expenses
FROM transactions;

total_income - 12032.34, total_expenses - 8435.99


What category did i spend the most money on?

SELECT c.name,
	   SUM(t.amount) as total_spent
FROM categories AS c
INNER JOIN transactions AS t
ON c.category_id = t.category_id
WHERE t.category_id != 1
GROUP BY c.name
ORDER BY total_spent DESC
LIMIT 1;

I spent the most on personal bills ($2820.00).


In which month did I spend the most money? 

SELECT
    EXTRACT(MONTH FROM date) AS month,
    SUM(amount) AS total_expenses
FROM transactions
WHERE category_id != 1
GROUP BY month
ORDER BY month;

I spent the most in July.


